{"nodes":[{"nodeID":"4567","text":"it may well be the case that an all-good God would want to create a world governed by natural law which includes the possibility of harm.","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:32:56"},{"nodeID":"4568","text":"if God creates a world that operates according to certain natural laws then the fire that warms us will also be the fire that burns us","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:32:56"},{"nodeID":"4569","text":"It would mean that you could drive as fast as you wanted on the highway","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:32:56"},{"nodeID":"4570","text":"you could drink or eat any substance you wanted to","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:32:56"},{"nodeID":"4571","text":"you could do anything to another person","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:32:56"},{"nodeID":"4572","text":"you could act anyway you want","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:32:56"},{"nodeID":"4573","text":"God did not want to create a world without harm","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:32:56"},{"nodeID":"4574","text":"The best world that could have been created was a world governed by natural laws","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:32:56"},{"nodeID":"4575","text":"if God were to create a world of free creatures in which He intervened every time to rescue us from harm this would be a world in which rational behavior was completely impossible.","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:32:56"},{"nodeID":"4576","text":"It would lead to total irresponsibility total irrationality in our actions.","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:32:56"},{"nodeID":"4577","text":"An irrational and irresponsable behaviour is not acceptable","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:32:56"},{"nodeID":"4578","text":"RA","type":"RA","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:32:56"},{"nodeID":"4579","text":"RA","type":"RA","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:32:56","scheme":"Example","schemeID":"14"},{"nodeID":"4580","text":"RA","type":"RA","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:32:57","scheme":"Example","schemeID":"14"},{"nodeID":"4581","text":"RA","type":"RA","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:32:57","scheme":"Example","schemeID":"14"},{"nodeID":"4582","text":"RA","type":"RA","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:32:57","scheme":"Example","schemeID":"14"},{"nodeID":"4583","text":"RA","type":"RA","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:32:58","scheme":"PracticalReasoning","schemeID":"28"},{"nodeID":"4584","text":"RA","type":"RA","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:32:58"}],"edges":[{"edgeID":"4295","fromID":"4568","toID":"4578","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"4296","fromID":"4578","toID":"4567","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"4297","fromID":"4569","toID":"4579","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"4298","fromID":"4579","toID":"4576","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"4299","fromID":"4570","toID":"4580","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"4300","fromID":"4580","toID":"4576","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"4301","fromID":"4571","toID":"4581","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"4302","fromID":"4581","toID":"4576","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"4303","fromID":"4572","toID":"4582","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"4304","fromID":"4582","toID":"4576","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"4305","fromID":"4573","toID":"4583","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"4306","fromID":"4574","toID":"4583","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"4307","fromID":"4583","toID":"4568","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"4308","fromID":"4575","toID":"4584","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"4309","fromID":"4576","toID":"4584","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"4310","fromID":"4577","toID":"4584","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"4311","fromID":"4584","toID":"4573","formEdgeID":null}],"locutions":[]}